OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of evening
OL,7,Fsunshine and staying dry overnight.
OL,8,FLow cloud and Haar could develop
OL,9,Faround the Angus coast overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright and
OL,12,Fvery warm inland. Low cloud and Haar
OL,13,Fcould affect some North Sea coasts.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,16,For some longer outbreaks of rain on
OL,17,FFriday and Saturday, the rain perhaps
OL,18,Fheavy and thundery at times. Early
OL,19,Frain clearing to scattered showers on
OL,20,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
